Description_lang: Sylvanas burdens targets with a ravenous affliction, inflicting $367607s1 Shadow damage every second. This effect stacks. Upon removal, this coalesces into a pool of shadow on the ground. Any player touching the pool gains $@spellname353929, consuming the pool.
AuraDescription_lang: $347607s1 Shadow damage inflicted every second.Coalesces upon the ground when removed for each stack.
